import React, {useCallback} from "react" import { Card, Tabs, Tab, Accordion, Button, ListGroup, Row, Col, Container, ToggleButtonGroup, ToggleButton, Breadcrumb, ButtonToolbar } from 'react-bootstrap' import "./Banner.css" import Romania from "../../../Images/romania.svg" import Italy from "../../../Images/italy.svg" import Upcom from "./Upcom/Upcom" import Live from "./Live/Live" import Finish from "./Finish/Finish" import {useDispatch, useSelector} from 'react-redux'; import isEqual from 'react-fast-compare'; import { SET_POSTS } from "../../../store/actions" import { useEffect, useState } from "react" const Banner = () => { const [showUrls, setShowUrls] = useState(false); const [activeIndex, setActiveIndex] = useState(-1); const [showCoeficents, setShowCoeficents] = useState(false); const [activeUrlIndex, setActiveUrlIndex] = useState(-1); const dispatch = useDispatch(); const posts = useSelector(state => state.posts, isEqual); const getPosts = useCallback(async () => { try { const fetchPosts = await fetch('http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/'); const res = await fetchPosts.json(); dispatch({ type: SET_POSTS, posts: JSON.parse(res.data) }); } catch (err) { console.log(err.message) } }, []); useEffect(() => { getPosts(); }, []) useEffect(() => { console.log(posts) }, [posts]) const onClickGame = (index) => { setActiveIndex(index); setShowUrls(!showUrls) } const onClickUrl = (index) => { setActiveUrlIndex(index); setShowCoeficents(true) } console.log(posts) return (
